  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK828">
<l>toḻutakai yuḷḷum paṭaiyoṭuṅku moṉṉā</l>
<l>raḻutakaṇ ṇīru maṉaittu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>A weapon may be hid in the very hands with which (one's) foes adore (him) (and) the tears they shed are of the same nature.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
